e>其實係咪兩個都啱</blockquote>裏係正體<br />\n裡係異體字，一般台灣人用多，由於電腦字係台灣做字，裡又比裏易整，所以初期電腦係冇裏得裡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家個裏字都係好底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714720e5898c872187e794cd0b74c127483cdbdc","tid":569542,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"小一個陣個老師教畢業個業字下面舊字係&quot;小&quot;新寫法就&quot;木&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪電腦子既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申利 : xp 電腦推出年代"},{"pid":"9be9252a5d283694adf68171d350fea4a123a968","tid":569542,"uid":129789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"究竟者字有冇一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef0f5b1b1aa3cf761f4cafdc82c28d95061f875","tid":569542,"uid":40445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=YDNRvebIfeXFhGVckbMWFY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c984c8ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E5%AD%97%E5%BD%A2%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n《常用字字形表》（下稱《字形表》；英文：List of Graphemes of Commonly-used Chinese Characters），是由香港教育署語文教育學院中文系（今歸作香港教育局和香港教育大學）制定的字形表，主編為李學銘。《字形表》收錄四千多個常用中文字的教育參考字形，應用於香港小學及初中識字教育及課本的中文字形印刷上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《字形表》比臺灣標準更合字源的例子編輯<br />\n<br />\n香港 裏：台灣 裡<br />\n香港 羣、峯： 台灣「群」、「峰」<br />\n吿、周、害：香港：三字豎筆下皆出頭，臺灣標準把三字內部訛作「土」字形<br />\n仲有好多例子"},{"pid":"4c3d38e49081ed244973388ed50e5d391fe89cec","tid":569542,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},